 Are you ready for the mind expander ? Ready to really know the reason behind the madness? Melting Runes Records presents their 10th release, "VA - Mind Expander"! This is a cooperation between Label DJ Yanik (Germany) and Label Manager Zemich (Denmark).

 The tracks are well selected to take you on a journey to the twisted, intelligent and dark depths of psychedelic music! So fasten your seat belts, take a deep breath and get ready to encounter the mind expanding reason of psygressive madness!

 We hope you enjoy this trippy journey as much as we do Thanks a lot to everyone involved in creating this compilation!
Mastered by Anti Logic Studio, Berlin, artwork by PANDORA Enjoy!
